keluarga Tian kami melalui pernikahan,

411
00:19:58,400 --> 00:20:00,750
Kita sudah mendaki melampaui posisi kita saat ini.

412
00:20:00,750 --> 00:20:02,400
Anda seharusnya senang dengan hal itu.

413
00:20:02,480 --> 00:20:03,270
Ayah,

414
00:20:03,480 --> 00:20:04,030
Sehat,

415
00:20:04,070 --> 00:20:05,830
Anda tahu temperamen Tuan Muda Sulung Luo.

416
00:20:05,830 --> 00:20:07,070
